These are the release notes for the Reviews extension.
	
Extension page on mediawiki.org: https://www.mediawiki.org/wiki/Extension:Reviews
Latest version of the release notes: http://svn.wikimedia.org/viewvc/mediawiki/trunk/extensions/Reviews/RELEASE-NOTES?view=co



=== Version 0.1 ===
(trunk)

Initial release with these features:

* People can post reviews on articles with one or more ratings attached.
* Review authors can view and edit their reviews.
* People with the can flag reviews.
* Admins can approve and delete reviews.
* Reviews can be sorted and filtered on various criteria.